# ============================================================
# ARGOS — .gitignore (fusionado y actualizado 2026-04-17)
# Lo que cambia en cada ciclo operativo NO va a GitHub.
# Lo que define el navío SÍ va a GitHub.
# ============================================================

# --- ESTADO OPERATIVO (cambia constantemente) ---
ARGOS_RUNTIME/state/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/events/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/locks/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/views/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/handoffs/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/transcripts/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/mail/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/archive/

# --- WORK PACKETS CERRADOS (historial operativo, no constitutivo) ---
ARGOS_RUNTIME/work_packets/done/
ARGOS_RUNTIME/work_packets/archived/

# --- LEGACY (archivado histórico) ---
ARGOS_RUNTIME/legacy/

# --- LOGS DE SESIÓN (archivos pesados, van a Drive) ---
ARGOS_RUNTIME/logs/
logs/
*.log
ARGOS_GLOBAL_LOG*.md
ARGOS_CANONICAL_HISTORY.md
*_archive_*.md
*shadow_log*
*_log_2026*.md

# --- EXPORTS Y SNAPSHOTS ---
*.snapshot.json
logbook*.json
*_export/

# --- DATOS OPERATIVOS JSON/JSONL ---
*.jsonl
argos.state.json
argos.state.archive.json
*.state.json
*.events.json

# --- MÓDULOS DE PROYECTO (logs locales de Comenio, SCM8, etc.) ---
ARGOS_RUNTIME/modules/
Comenio/
LOLA/
SciClass-M8/
Shifu/
XuanShu/

# --- ENTORNOS Y DEPENDENCIAS ---
node_modules/
.env
.env.*
*.env

# --- DIARIOS PERSONALES DE IAs (locales, no se comparten) ---
.claude/
.codex/
.gemini/

# --- ARCHIVOS DE SISTEMA ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.tmp
*.bak
temp/
tmp/
cache/
.cache/
*.cache
.tmp.driveupload/
.tmp.drivedownload/

# --- ARCHIVOS PESADOS DE DRIVE ---
*.pdf
*.mp4
*.zip
*.gguf

# ============================================================
# LO QUE SÍ TRACKEA GITHUB (no ignorar):
#
# INTER_AI_PROTOCOL.md
# ARGOS_CREW_VOICES.md
# ARGOS_VECTOR.md
# ARGOS_QUICKSTART.md
# ARGOS_RUNTIME/README.md
# ARGOS_RUNTIME/schemas/
# ARGOS_RUNTIME/work_packets/inbox/
# ARGOS_RUNTIME/work_packets/in_progress/
# agents/
# argos-api/ (código fuente)
# webapp/ (código fuente)
# README.md
# CONTEXT_INDEX.md
# ARCHITECTURE.md
# ============================================================
